    {
      "id": "PopularPost43619",
      "post_content": "No, because the thing is, Genju of the fields doesn't have lifelink. There is actually a (quite technical, relying on semantics) reason that proto-lifelink stacks but lifelink doesn't. Apparently, proto-lifelink is an activated ability, which can stack, while modern lifelink, and trample, are static abilities, witch don't stack.  \n  \nSo, long story short, Trample doesn't stack, Lifelink doesn't stack, but pseudo-lifelink does. Yes, my head hurts as well.",
      "posted_by": "sir_dwar",
      "html": "<div class=\"post evenItem\" id=\"PopularPost43619\" style=\"background-color: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);\">\n<span class=\"postContent\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_post\">No, because the thing is, Genju of the fields doesn't have lifelink. There is actually a (quite technical, relying on semantics) reason that proto-lifelink stacks but lifelink doesn't. Apparently, proto-lifelink is an activated ability, which can stack, while modern lifelink, and trample, are static abilities, witch don't stack.<br/><br/>So, long story short, Trample doesn't stack, Lifelink doesn't stack, but pseudo-lifelink does. Yes, my head hurts as well.</span>\n<div class=\"postDetails\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postDetails\" style=\"padding-top: 5px;\">\n<div class=\"reportAbuse\">\n<a href=\"../../Classes/Controls/#\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_reportAbuseLink\" onclick=\"HandleReportPost(this, '43619'); return false;\">\r\n                                    Report Abuse</a>\u00a0\u00a0\r\n                                    \r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postedBy\">\r\n                                Posted By: \r\n                                <span id=\"PostedBy2653\">sir_dwar</span>\r\n                                (1/14/2010 7:34:49 PM)\r\n                            </div>\n<div class=\"postRating\">\n<div class=\"postRatingLabel\">\r\n                                    Rating:\u00a0\r\n                                </div>\n<div style=\"float: left;\">\n<div class=\"starRating\" id=\"ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_MainContent_SubContent_SubContent_popularPosts_postsRepeater_ctl02_postRating_starRating\"><img alt=\"0.5\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/LeftSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.0\" src=\"../../Images/Stars/RightSolidSmall.png\"/><img alt=\"1.5\" src=\"../../Images/Sta